-- All declarations of the package are imported into the local namespace of another package.

END TC3;

PACKAGE pckgId::pckgId::pckgId
    PUBLIC
        THREAD threadTypeId
        END threadTypeId;
        
        THREAD threadTypeId

END pckgId::pckgId::pckgId;
